reviewText: Was a European DVD and could not be played. Neglected to give that info

I wanted to see this picture ever since I heard about Dido about a year ago. I am from the West Indies. When I google searched her they said she was from Nevis which is the island I lived close to but it wasn't as sure states. Which I knew which island in the Caribbean she was from. But over all a very nice and educational movie.
